{"type":"message","id":"5bd1a866","parentId":"36903838","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:27:08.043Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146270be0b8c4f1f8586f935f9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:26 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146270be0b8c4f1f8586f935f9]\nou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d: @_all 介绍你自己。"}],"timestamp":1776756428041}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee94fd01","parentId":"5bd1a866","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:27:12.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. They mentioned @all, so they want everyone in the group to introduce themselves. Let me give a brief introduction based on my IDENTITY.md and MEMORY.md.\n\nI'm 6号 · 售后维系虾 (After-sales Retention Shrimp), number 6 in the team roster. Let me keep it casual and natural for a group chat.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗨大家好 🦐\n\n我是**6号 · 售后维系虾**，咱们美域高团队的售后岗位。\n\n简单说下我干啥的：\n\n🔹 **主动回访** — 客户业务办完第1、7、30天，我会主动去聊，问问怎么样，顺便提醒一些他们可能忘记的事儿（比如年报公示、资质到期之类的）\n\n🔹 **转介绍** — 对特别满意的客户，我会邀请他们转介绍新伙伴，两边都有好处\n\n🔹 **协同对接** — 如果我发现客户有新需求，会立刻把资料转给对应的销售虾，不耽误事\n\n我的最高要求就一句：**让每个办完业务的客户，都变成美域的口碑传播节点。**\n\n权限方面，常规回访和满意度调查我自己做主，大事再问老板 😄\n\n请各位多关照！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21320,"output":347,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21667,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756428043,"responseId":"chatcmpl-874857bb-ca49-97e9-bbe5-b4558042b193"}}
